TextChange: Should modern society be criticized for its materialism?\n\n

Though I do not necessarily blame the people in society for their materialism (we are all socially and systemically conditioned to think over-consumption is okay, or even a good thing), we all have a part to play in it. It will take the efforts of all of us to undo this problem and help spare our planet, and our minds, from overconsumption and excessive materialism.
